PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Finance of PAUL MASSICOTTE, of Mount Royal, Quebec, BARBARA R. HISLOP, of Vancouver, British Columbia, and HAROLD HUGH MacKAY, of Regina, Saskatchewan, as directors of the Board of Directors of the Bank of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective March 1, 2001.
